# EMOTA vision (planning)

Before **planning**, **roadmaps**, **architecture proposals**, **multi-file refactors**, or **scoping new subsystems**:

1. Read **`VISION.md`** at the repo root — product north star, scale limits, anti-drift list.
2. Then **`AGENTS.md`** and **`.agents/skills/emota/SKILL.md`** for paths and stack.

Do not start large plans without checking VISION.md pillars (mobile-first, solo trail + optional live wall, no signup wall, per-class scale path — not one global room at national scale).
